story.title: My Fiance's Brother - Episode 3

messages.text: How could you do this to me?
God, did you see his face?
Just like I saw you running down the aisle.
You had nothing to do with it.
I had everything to with it.
I never should have told you.
I should have just married Blake.
Because that‚Äôs what I was supposed to do.
Your dad threatened to kill me.
I shouldn‚Äôt have looked at you the way I did.
You mean like your heart was breaking?
Everyone looked at me when I ran off.
But then I was gone ‚Äî I got off easy.
No one moved for the longest time.
Then one of Blake‚Äôs groomsmen called you a whore.
I punched him in the face.
I‚Äôm the one who walked out on the groom!
The same groom who cheated on you.
That doesn‚Äôt make what we did any better.
I need time. And I need to see Blake.
You may have stopped the wedding.
But we‚Äôre still going to be parents.
Give HIM time ‚Äî or give YOU time?
We need each other more than ever.
I know what I did sucked.
But I was trying to do the right thing.
This is just a lot to take in.
Which is why I want to be with you.
J, I‚Äôm supposed to be at my reception.
I‚Äôm supposed to be at the bar getting wrecked.
I never imagined you‚Äôd do that.
Maybe. But why did you have to do THAT?
I know. It‚Äôs about the baby, too.
If you knew that, why did you object?
I was objecting to the lies.
The love you and Blake share is a lie.
I haven‚Äôt been able to stop.
Just not in the way he needed me to.
Blake just sent me a text.
He‚Äôs pissed and wants to talk.
